            . I heard the witness cry Stop thief! and saw the prisoner run; I pursued, and took him.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I had not been out of my bed ten minutes; I live nearly opposite the church: I was going up Monmouth-street, and the man stopped me, and asked if I was the person; the witness said he was not certain.</p>
